{"tid":708224,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人真係好撚on9","createTime":"2018-06-19T07:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T12:16:45.000Z","uid":141782,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5acc5856ef2c93124d202b65ddd76107407d2fd","tid":708224,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"喺西班牙<br />\n影影下相有個支那導遊行過黎<br />\n佢:china? China?<br />\n我:no<br />\n佢:korea?<br />\n我: Hong kong<br />\n佢: Hong kong is..中國的..china 呀<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  行撚開眼尾都唔望佢<br />\n跟住佢班團友行到過黎 問個導遊我係咪中國人<br />\n佢:er...佢話佢係香港人唔係中國人喎<br />\n跟住班支那狗開始汪汪聲話香港是中國的呀, 就開始鬧個導遊<br />\n導遊:這不是我說的呀是人家說的呀<br />\n<br />\n成班狗凈係圍埋一邊汪汪聲發掹憎, 又唔敢當面屌柒我<br />\n個大媽仲掹到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既樣<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝打開新聞見到侵侵當支那狗咁撚真係心情愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ca74d77f2d2e2a3b1228aaae6d91d0df3b345d","tid":708224,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"絲打好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17166c20e4d29d6439931e89c3f7da527b1cdcf6","tid":708224,"uid":134779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ed97ce9cb48a691ef5237795ca7a0949b6ecf6","tid":708224,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T11:37:01.000Z","msg":"做乜成團人都想知你邊度人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01559c1e5cf56bae93859e56163770005de0fda7","tid":708224,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9ed97ce9cb48a691ef5237795ca7a0949b6ecf6","tid"